        Updated 2019-04-04
    //-
    #fpge
        +name('FPGE - Functional Post Game Ending', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/66726', 'fnv')
        +modInfo
            +author Kazopert
            +version 1.3
            +installation Install #[+file('Functional Post Game Ending')] and #[+file('Functional Post Game Ending - Outside Bets Patch')]
            +notes Reviewing Outside Bets Patch

    //-
        Gunsmithing
        Updated 2019-03-22
    //-
    #gunsmithing
        +name('Gunsmithing', 'https://www.nexusmods.com/newvegas/mods/50312', 'ttw')
        +modInfo
            +author Puppettron
            +version 4.4.2
            +installation Install the #[+file('Gunsmithing TTW')] optional file
            +notes
                | A smallish mod that adds gunsmithing to NV, so you can break down and build weapons your damn self,
                | instead of relying on NPCs all the time.
    //-
        More Spawns
        Updated 2019-04-02
    //-
    #more-spawns
        +name('More Spawns', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ATP_TnysYYKFZ2LPsSHRT45kgCpyiLeJ/view?usp=sharing', 'ttw')
        +modInfo
            +author FiftyTifty
            +installation Install #[+file('More Spawns.7z')]
            +optional
                | Double click More Spawns in the left pane and go to the [Optional ESPs] tab.
                | Move the 3x version to the "Optional ESPs" box.
            +notes
                | Increases spawns around the Wasteland. More info on
                | #[+link('the TTW forum post', 'https://taleoftwowastelands.com/viewtopic.php?t=6678')]

